data.description: WELCOME TO A BEAUTIFUL, WELL LOVED HOME NESTLED IN THE HEART OF GIBRALTAR, CONVENIENTLY LOCATED NEAR FABULOUS RESTAURANTS, MARINA'S, LAKE ERIE METROPARK, BIKE PATHS & MUCH MORE! FRSHLY PAINTED & BRAND NEW CARPET THROUGHOUT WITH A COZY NATURAL FIREPLACE IN THE FAMILY ROOM, A LARGE LIVING ROOM THAT CAN BE USED AS A DINING ROOM, AN EAT IN KITCHEN, 3 BEDROOMS,2 BATHROOMS, AN OFFICE/DEN, & 2 CAR GARAGE. IT BOASTS AN EXTRA LARGE LOT WITH AN AREA TO PLANT VEGETABLES, SURROUNDED BY GORGEOUS ESTABLISHED PERENNIALS. ORIGINAL OWNER. NEVER BEEN ON THE MARKET BEFORE. THIS PROPERTY WILL NOT LAST LONG!
